{"tid":267333,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"[又來] - 一個袋有30個波, 3種色, 最少抽幾多個波可以有哂3隻色？","createTime":"2017-06-02T08:08:35.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-03T14:04:39.000Z","uid":68138,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"4c1d5c7fc5632571a753dd4e46f3bc5fdb509e5e","tid":267333,"uid":68138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-02T08:08:35.000Z","msg":"小學雞問題<br />\n<br />\n一個袋有30個波<br />\n10 藍 10 紅 10 綠<br />\n<br />\n每次拎一個 唔會放返落袋 個波一拎左出黎就即刻知佢咩色<br />\n<br />\n最少拎幾多個波可以有哂3隻色？"},{"pid":"5bc6946980f80852c2b76555972d8b5089ea3c58","tid":267333,"uid":53794,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-02T08:09:33.000Z","msg":"3"},{"pid":"36627e9abb2cbbf200dfc671651385db3ef6cd98","tid":267333,"uid":53794,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-02T08:09:55.000Z","msg":"唔係喎 1"},{"pid":"c8efa26c3a155c8d653d4575310fd0de9173d3ea","tid":267333,"uid":68138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-02T08:10:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>3</blockquote><br />\n咁快有人答...."},{"pid":"f87315d9a54cf0c70440f8b6ae525d9b8e483f88","tid":267333,"uid":63311,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-02T08:10:54.000Z","msg":"3個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8785e699ed0e91f3e278d69da9717e99080b17cc","tid":267333,"uid":68138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-02T08:11:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔係喎 1</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n請問點解係1呢?"},{"pid":"ab16a369e2d28c37ecce6ae8705221f52e0210ea","tid":267333,"uid":68138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-02T08:11:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>3個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n請問點解係3呢?"},{"pid":"b937406b593f99b265ae2016752057383d0379b9","tid":267333,"uid":45000,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-02T08:11:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>唔係喎 1</blockquote><